                            <p>

                                This section, through direct coordination with Ministry of Transport, communication and IT, issues navigation warnings and notices to all the users to ensure safe navigation in Omani water.
                                <br />  <br />
                                As soon as these information are reported through local sources as ports, RNO vessels, RAO and other crafts, informing navigation danger, information and location are made on the chart.
                                <br />  <br />
