                                <br />  <br />
                                In addition, this draft is also sent to Pakistan Hydro Office, as it is the responsible authority of the ninth region, to be transmitted through SAFETY NET.
                                <br />  <br />
                                Moreover, the section also publishes half monthly notices to mariners to be benefit for Oman’s ships and monthly notices to mariners distributed to users of Oman Navigational charts to be corrected.



                            </p>

